casebody.data:
The GULF REFINING COMPANY, Appellant, v. Louis W. FETSCHAN, Appellee. No. 7273. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. Nov. 8, 1937. Maxwell & Ramsey, of Cincinnati, Ohio, for appellant. Harry A. Abr.ams, Frank R. Gusweiler, and Ralph B. Kohnen, all of Cincinnati, Ohio, for appellee.

Before MOORMAN, SIMONS, and ALLEN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

It is ordered that the appeal in this cause be, and the same is, dismissed, pursuant to motion of counsel for appellant
